Package com.mouseviator.fsuipc

Interface IFSUIPCListener

  • public interface IFSUIPCListener
    This interface to be implemented to receive notifications from FSUIPC library. Use FSUIPC.addListener(com.mouseviator.fsuipc.IFSUIPCListener) to add implemented listener.
    Author:
    Mouseviator

      • onProcess

        void onProcess​(java.util.AbstractQueue<IDataRequest> arRequests)
        This function will be called every time the FSUIPC_Process function is being called.Ie. every time the library actually instructs FSUIPC to exchange data.
        Parameters:
        arRequests - A queue of requests that has been processed. This will be only requests stored int the continual requests queue. The "one-time" requests queue is discarded after every successful processing.
